# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# F90+ — Environment template
# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in. NEVER commit `.env.local` (it is gitignored).
#
# The foundation phase needs NONE of these. They are placeholders that document
# the integrations planned on the roadmap so the wiring is obvious later.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# App — canonical site URL (used for metadata, OG/Twitter cards, sitemap, robots).
# Local dev: leave as-is. PRODUCTION (Vercel): set to https://f90.xyz
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"

